<title>USA: Glasgal Q3 Jan 31 loss narrows slightly.</title>
<headline>Glasgal Q3 Jan 31 loss narrows slightly.</headline>
<dateline>FAIRFIELD, N.J. 1997-03-24</dateline>
<text>
<p>3 Months Ended	   9 Months Ended</p>
<p>				January 31		January 31</p>
<p>			   1997	  1996	1997	  1996</p>
<p>Total Sales	   21,355	26,097    73,965	89,055</p>
<p>Oper Profit (Loss)  (2,016)     (1,875)	536	   685</p>
<p>Net Loss	     (2,271)     (2,295)     (844)     (1,166)</p>
<p>EPS			(.11)	 (.12)     (.04)	 (.07)</p>
<p>NOTE: The company's full name is Glasgal Communications Inc.</p>
<p>Glasgal's sales backlog is currently running at approximately $31.6 million compared to $28.2 million at the same time last year.</p>
<p>((-- New York Newsdesk   212-859-1610))</p>
